Myriam Léonie Mani (amụrụ na Mee 21, 1977) bụ onye Cameroon na-eme egwuregwu nke maara nke ọma na mita 100 na 200.
Mani nọchitere anya Cameroon na 2008 Summer Olympics na-asọmpi na 100 mita sprint
Na agba nke mbụ ya, ọ nọ n'ọkwa nke atọ n'azụ Torri Edwards na Jeanette Kwakye na oge nke 11.64 iji gaa n'ihu na agba nke abụọ
N'ebe ahụ, o rughị eru maka ọkara ikpeazụ n'ihi na oge ya nke 11.65 bụ naanị oge nke isii nke okpomọkụ ya, na-akpata mwepụ.
